            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftträger: the base is made of two joined, reused architrave blocks. Base used two times: IRT 283 carved over IRT 423, only superficially erased. Buchstabenhöhe: IRT 423: 4-5; IRT 283: 4-8. Datierung: IRT 423: von 202; IRT 283: 250-300.</p>
